N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 5901.3 - Grant awards

State Regulations

The office may award, on a competitive basis, grants to match
funds expended by regional high technology development organizations for the
purposes set forth herein and in requests for proposals issued by the
office. Notes
